snippet.title: Celebrities Who Confronted Amber Heard In Person
snippet.description:
►Celebrities Who Confronted Amber Heard In Person 
For years, Johnny Depp and his ex-wife Amber Heard have been embroiled in various court fights, and it appears that the drama is finally coming to a conclusion. The actor's legal team has requested subpoenas for Amber's ex-boyfriend, spacex billionaire Elon Musk, and the ACLU in the latest move in Johnny's $50 million defamation action against Amber. Amber agreed to donate half of her $7 million divorce settlement to a non-profit charity. Johnny's attorneys believe they have proof that Amber lied about donating the money to charity and are demanding depositions from Musk and the Aclu representatives, as well as all paperwork related to their dealings with Amber.
